  "detailed_description": "<h1>Developer's message</h1><p>Hello, knights! We are 'Olive Panda' an internal game studio under ChengDu LongYou Tech Ltd. We are the development team of 'Krzyżacy - The Knights of the Cross'.<br>We are a group of passionate indie game enthusiasts who have come together because of a shared gaming dream. Our goal is to create a highly anticipated indie game and contribute to the development of the gaming industry.<br>From the project's inception to its unveiling today, our journey has been filled with changes. We have reset the storyline, revamped combat mechanics, all in pursuit of delivering a better gaming experience. The game showcases a unique art style inspired by exquisite pixel art, and we have meticulously crafted pixel art illustrations to bring the characters, composed entirely of pixels, to life in a more  vivid way.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Krzyżacy - The Knights of the Cross is a unique, story-driven deckbuilding RPG game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/6fe1b079b09d5a044c4393d6c0098597.poster.avif?t=1728975859\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/6fe1b079b09d5a044c4393d6c0098597.webm?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/6fe1b079b09d5a044c4393d6c0098597.mp4?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story is adapted from the Nobel Prize-winning work “Krzyżacy - The Knights of the Cross” by Henryk Sienkiewicz, and tell the life and death struggles between the Polish-Lithuanian people and the aggressive Teutonic Knights in the 15th century. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a knight, embark on the medieval adventure, search for companions, collect diverse cards, and help Polish-Lithuanian Alliance defeat the Teutonic Knights in the Battle of Grunwald.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/256617d6cfbb3ce0d9f46e28b4c0c9f3.avif?t=1728975859\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/bc0d41dff862370d18221f542a212c12.poster.avif?t=1728975859\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/bc0d41dff862370d18221f542a212c12.webm?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/bc0d41dff862370d18221f542a212c12.mp4?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet over 30 unique teammates! Pirate captain from the sea, alchemist seeking the philosopher's stone, or noble lady aspiring to be a knight... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 30 teammates have their own storylines. By completing the storylines, you can learn about their personalities and pasts, and get their exclusive cards or relics.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some teammates can only be recruited conditionally. Leveling up, unlocking achievements, or completing specific tasks. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/c1944108dd4f519e0c20d41682a8b1d9.avif?t=1728975859\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/f239dea6c7d4c2790ca9b377ad905a1e.poster.avif?t=1728975859\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/f239dea6c7d4c2790ca9b377ad905a1e.webm?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/f239dea6c7d4c2790ca9b377ad905a1e.mp4?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruited teammates are the game changer with their exclusive skills. The ultra skills’ special effects spice up the battles further!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every teammate has beautiful pixel-art portraits and 2D live animations.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Teammates can release their exclusive skills with stunning special effects, and they are triggered by the way you play cards. Strategize your cards and teammates to maximize your battle capacity! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/6e79b990bf7ce4702315d1a8e0d571f9.avif?t=1728975859\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/237983c45019f73304c9bab74889d534.poster.avif?t=1728975859\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/237983c45019f73304c9bab74889d534.webm?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/237983c45019f73304c9bab74889d534.mp4?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategize and create builds centering characters skills! Preferring active teammate skills as often as possible, or playing a safer way with more defenses, is up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the right cards, teammates, and relics to create your unique combat styles. Teammates will respond to your card actions.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Teammates will respond to the player's card actions and record the skill points used when playing cards, determining their own actions during the match.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bosses also have special mechanisms. They increase the cost of specific cards or remove debuffs. Developing a strategy to beat them!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/813a336fa56efbf3d26be7ee741d8254.avif?t=1728975859\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/55b101f8fddcbbb0869f259a60b3f10a.poster.avif?t=1728975859\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/55b101f8fddcbbb0869f259a60b3f10a.webm?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/55b101f8fddcbbb0869f259a60b3f10a.mp4?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as noble Zbyszko in the main storyline and embark on a medieval adventure, meet two heroines, and confront the formidable Teutonic Knights…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A medieval historic scroll with 7 chapters and over 200 side requests and events.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different choices lead to different storylines. Can you save the kind lord's daughter Danusia?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traditional festivals and medieval folk lifestyles are included in the random plots of the game. Get rewards and learn about the life pictures of medieval people.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/465fc3a5f5d598e1d2dc5814edf699cc.avif?t=1728975859\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/2e7119a0ad003dac2407232f3254eec5.poster.avif?t=1728975859\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/2e7119a0ad003dac2407232f3254eec5.webm?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/2e7119a0ad003dac2407232f3254eec5.mp4?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For better in-game experience of historical storytelling and combat, and to further immerse them into the adventure, we introduce the new 'Character Pack (Western Style)'. This pack is created to cater to players' demand for different art styles and allowing players to freely choose whether to use it in the game or not.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Krzyżacy - The Knights of the Cross is a unique, story-driven deckbuilding RPG game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/6fe1b079b09d5a044c4393d6c0098597.poster.avif?t=1728975859\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/6fe1b079b09d5a044c4393d6c0098597.webm?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/6fe1b079b09d5a044c4393d6c0098597.mp4?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story is adapted from the Nobel Prize-winning work “Krzyżacy - The Knights of the Cross” by Henryk Sienkiewicz, and tell the life and death struggles between the Polish-Lithuanian people and the aggressive Teutonic Knights in the 15th century. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a knight, embark on the medieval adventure, search for companions, collect diverse cards, and help Polish-Lithuanian Alliance defeat the Teutonic Knights in the Battle of Grunwald.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/256617d6cfbb3ce0d9f46e28b4c0c9f3.avif?t=1728975859\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/bc0d41dff862370d18221f542a212c12.poster.avif?t=1728975859\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i