ra skills’ special effects spice up the battles further!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every teammate has beautiful pixel-art portraits and 2D live animations.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Teammates can release their exclusive skills with stunning special effects, and they are triggered by the way you play cards. Strategize your cards and teammates to maximize your battle capacity! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/6e79b990bf7ce4702315d1a8e0d571f9.avif?t=1728975859\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/237983c45019f73304c9bab74889d534.poster.avif?t=1728975859\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/237983c45019f73304c9bab74889d534.webm?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/237983c45019f73304c9bab74889d534.mp4?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategize and create builds centering characters skills! Preferring active teammate skills as often as possible, or playing a safer way with more defenses, is up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the right cards, teammates, and relics to create your unique combat styles. Teammates will respond to your card actions.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Teammates will respond to the player's card actions and record the skill points used when playing cards, determining their own actions during the match.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bosses also have special mechanisms. They increase the cost of specific cards or remove debuffs. Developing a strategy to beat them!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/813a336fa56efbf3d26be7ee741d8254.avif?t=1728975859\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/55b101f8fddcbbb0869f259a60b3f10a.poster.avif?t=1728975859\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/55b101f8fddcbbb0869f259a60b3f10a.webm?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/55b101f8fddcbbb0869f259a60b3f10a.mp4?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as noble Zbyszko in the main storyline and embark on a medieval adventure, meet two heroines, and confront the formidable Teutonic Knights…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A medieval historic scroll with 7 chapters and over 200 side requests and events.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different choices lead to different storylines. Can you save the kind lord's daughter Danusia?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traditional festivals and medieval folk lifestyles are included in the random plots of the game. Get rewards and learn about the life pictures of medieval people.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/465fc3a5f5d598e1d2dc5814edf699cc.avif?t=1728975859\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/2e7119a0ad003dac2407232f3254eec5.poster.avif?t=1728975859\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/2e7119a0ad003dac2407232f3254eec5.webm?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092850/extras/2e7119a0ad003dac2407232f3254eec5.mp4?t=1728975859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For better in-game experience of historical storytelling and combat, and to further immerse them into the adventure, we introduce the new 'Character Pack (Western Style)'. This pack is created to cater to players' demand for different art styles and allowing players to freely choose whether to use it in the game or not.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
